    <abstract>
      <t>The purpose of this memo is to initiate a discussion for a migration path of the WAIS technology from Z39.50-1988 Information Retrieval Service Definitions and Protocol Specification for Library Applications [1] to Z39.50-1992 [2] and then to Z39.50-1994 [3].  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.</t>
